      <p class="- topic/p ">You can provide the following information on the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Qualifications and Benefits</b> page:</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <table class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="col1" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col2" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Fields</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Description</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Bundle Name</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Select the bundle name for the set of products you want to buy.</p>
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Mention the package name for the set of products, for which package is created, you want to buy.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Product Name</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Add products or categories in the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Product Name</b> column. For adding products or categories, please refer to the <xref href="../adding-products_102432695_102432695/102432695.dita"
                                 format="dita"
                                 class="- topic/xref ">Adding Products</xref> section. Products are the list of products that are purchased by customers at the bundle level.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">UOM (Unit Of Measure)</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">It defaults to <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Each.</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Type</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Auto-populated based on selected products or categories.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Unit</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the unit of products that customer purchases.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Unit Price</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the price of the products per unit.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Extended Price</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">It is the auto-calculated price for the whole unit of the product.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Bundle Price</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Aggregated price of the products which are grouped in the bundle.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Save</b>
                        </p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <p class="- topic/p ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Save</b> to save the made changes.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can also import the bundle product by duplicate the entire bundle to perform the following actions:</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">To add multiple bundles to the programs</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">To edit the start and end dates</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">To add new products to the bundles</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="- topic/p ">For more information about Tiered qualifications and benefits, please refer to the <xref href="../qualifications_and_benefi_102432700/102432700.dita"
               format="dita"
               class="- topic/xref ">Qualifications and Benefits</xref> section.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">
         <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Importing Benefit Line Items</b>
      </p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">For more information about importing the individual section of the Package Saving Program, please refer to the <xref href="../importing_benefit_line_it_102432715/102432715.dita"
               format="dita"
               class="- topic/xref ">Importing Benefit Line Items</xref> section.</p>
